    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted given that the single ASTM F1717 offset distance tested is the regulatory standard condition and the primary basis for the submission decision. All three QoIs satisfy both quantitative acceptance criteria across the full N=11 ensemble. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level conclusion for this COU.",
